---
---
<html lang="es" style="scroll-behavior: smooth;">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Jes&uacute;sDevtech | Digital Architect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;600;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #030712; color: #fff; margin: 0; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav style="padding: 2rem 10%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
        <div style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.05em;">JES&Uacute;S<span class="gradient-text">DEVTECH</span></div>
        <a href="#contacto" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 8px;">CONTACTAR</a>
    </nav>

    <header style="padding: 10rem 10% 5rem 10%;">
        <h1 style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 15vw, 10rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 0.8; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase;">
            JES&Uacute;S<br/><span style="color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 2px #fff;">MANUEL</span>
        </h1>
        <div style="margin-top: 3rem; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.2rem;">
            Ingeniero en Software & Ciberseguridad. Especialista en crear ecosistemas digitales escalables, sistemas de IA local y auditorías de seguridad ofensiva.
        </div>
    </header>

    <section style="padding: 5rem 10%; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        {[ {t: 'Inteligencia Artificial', d: 'Desarrollo de modelos offline tipo LLM con Transformers.js.'}, {t: 'Seguridad Ofensiva', d: 'Auditorías de pentesting con Kali Linux y bases de datos.'}, {t: 'Mobile Dev', d: 'Aplicaciones nativas de alto rendimiento con Flutter.'} ].map(card => (
            <div class="glass" style="padding: 3rem; border-radius: 20px; transition: 0.4s;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-10px)'; this.style.borderColor='#38bdf8'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='translateY(0)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.05)'">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0;">{card.t}</h3>
                <p style="color: #64748b;">{card.d}</p>
            </div>
        ))}
    </section>

    <footer id="contacto" style="padding: 10rem 10%; text-align: center;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #38bdf8; font-weight: 600;">¿Tienes un proyecto en mente?</p>
        <h2 style="font-size: 4rem; margin: 1rem 0;">Hablemos.</h2>
        <a href="https://wa.me/526952395801" style="background: #fff; color: #000; padding: 1.5rem 3rem; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 900; display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem;">INICIAR PROYECTO</a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>